		Thế thì $\displaystyle \int\limits_0^{\tfrac{\pi}{2}}{\sin (2x)}\text{e}^{\sin^2x}\text{\,d}x=\displaystyle\int\limits_{0}^{1} \text{e}^u \text{\,d}u$.
	}

